    "description": "<p>Rockmann is established since the early eighties, catering to all construction related works. We have sucessfully transformed from a small renovation company to a Design & Build Construction Company. With our very own in-house designers, artists, architects and engineers, We're able to accomodate to any customer's expectation.</p>\n\n<p>We take pride in all our works and has therefore established a reputation for providing high quality craftsmanship and customer satisfactory products throughout Asia and the Middle East.With more than 20 years expertise in this field and the knowledge and technology in this field, we hope to realise our customer's dreams.We specialise in GFRC Rockworks, Design & Build, Landscaping, Waterfeature, Pools, Ponds and Filtration System.</p>\n",
